<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF976A28F7F3955616D8B895" pageId="108" pageNumber="866" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF976A28F7F3955616D8B895" blockId="108.[2062,2657,709,1131]" pageId="108" pageNumber="866">
Previously considered a race of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF976A28F62695561639B86A" baseAuthorityName="J. Fischer" baseAuthorityYear="1829" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Plecotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="108" pageNumber="866" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="austriacus">P. austriacus</taxonomicName>
, but raised to full species status based on genetic and morphological differences. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
